    public class MainWindowController
extends AbstractController
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    This class is the controller class for MainView.fxml It holds all logics for user interface such as on screen buttons.

        Parameters:
        modelAccess - The model access of the Timeline Manager
        timelineViewer - The timelineViewer that shows all Timelines and tasks on the main window
